name: The Empress
description:
The Empress Tarot card shows us a woman who is fanning herself. That means you should be relax and not worry about your annoying thoughts.
The Bird is beside to Empress’ head so this tells us instead of get lost in your annoying thoughts you should see and catch up lucky events.
The Stars means that you will live your lucky side of your life you will shine as a star but first of all you should see your lucky bird first.
On the corner there is a snake and it means you start searching a meaning for your life because of that, be carefull jealous people can come up.
But if you hold out them a olive branch, all eyes will be on you.
